snippet.title: amancalledjoel
snippet.description:
This is my channel containing different topics by many different people.  With great gratitude I share the works of Stephan Molyneux and Jed Mckenna in particular as well as all others.
If I could write or create quality videos, I would.  Thankfully, other people have talent as I only have interest and intent to share.
